Build Instructions for Fedora 24

(recomended, update all packages to latest version)
# dnf dist distro-sync

Install Standard C Development Group
# dnf groupinstall "C Development Tools and Libraries"

Install Additional Development Packages
# dnf install cmake libsodium-devel boost-devel

$ git clone https://github.com/yedino/galaxy42.git
$ cd galaxy42
$ ./do
